[URL=http://www.project-fnatic.net][IMG]http://i429.photobucket.com/albums/qq20/nathanz1_2008/banner1_zpsa92d6848.png[/img][/URL]
[size=12pt]Introduction:[/size]
Hello and welcome to the project fnatic thread. Project Fnatic has been around for about 2 years but today is releasing the latest project fnatic server. Project Fnatic is brought to you for your enjoyment and is made for the players. I have been working on it for about 2 weeks and it is still in progress but is at the point of releasing in BETA.
[size=14pt][b]About Project Fnatic:[/b][/size]
In project Fnatic you have a easy start, you will be given 10 PKP and 7 million coins which you can spend in the stores situated in edgeville. You can recieve PKP from dueling, pking or completing slayer tasks. Content will be getting added daily and i hope for players to make there suggestions known on our vbulletin forum. The server is fluid, has flawless gameplay and will be around as long as the players are happy.
[font=impact]Features:[/font]
Pk points shop Vote shop Many shops in edgeville Flawless combat Custom training dungeon Alot of donator benefits New items such as d claws, vesta, korasi's sword, armadyl Npc clipping Custom skilling island in progress perfect specials duel arena webclient with xat MANY PKING SPOTS INCLUDING FALADOR PVP Come and see
